{"tid":1806981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日遊行見到，市民見到「香港獨立」旗隊係歡呼","createTime":"2020-01-01T14:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T14:44:50.000Z","uid":34869,"like":192,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"bd72a272e48ca5186078e760bd693bf05f4cee88","tid":1806981,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"香港人經過2014年，到今年終於做到和勇不分<br />\n立場之前篇文就提出「獨立」同「民主」有機會成為下一個分割點<br />\n<br />\n但今日睇到「香港獨立」旗隊行過既時候，其他市民唔係屌佢地鬼，而係歡呼<br />\n雖然我同意有啲野係要靜靜地做，但今日當做民意調查，證明大家又進化左<br />\n<br />\n當時梁匪689響立法會提出「港獨」呢一隻稻草人，就係想泛民/老一輩同下一代割蓆<br />\n但結果搞搞下將所有野都打為「港獨」，令民意推到去意識到唯一出路<br />\n<br />\n新一年，各位手足繼續努力"},{"pid":"94dc533b1d3c1cd969e1975dfb853206a08f61da","tid":1806981,"uid":35456,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"624540df4417ec918b16fff9f87300b64fbbaaab","tid":1806981,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4934b25c5ea1879709ce74cadc7b5ad23fababe","tid":1806981,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:59:18.000Z","msg":"中共同港共係一定會弄假成真"},{"pid":"01673477add421caed686c4b24a7b967adb97421","tid":1806981,"uid":116054,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:01:57.000Z","msg":"同埋政府見咁多人撐獨，民陣又唔割<br />\n<br />\n今日冷處理港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384c9a54b3ca48360bce09ae441ee7ccc9508d16","tid":1806981,"uid":157522,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:03:35.000Z","msg":"雖然我同意有啲野係要靜靜地做<br />\n<br />\n我都覺，<br />\n怕係怕老一輩接受唔到會割"},{"pid":"c4ecaeccf8e616a3eb83955e8a9e8071154ba9f6","tid":1806981,"uid":187201,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"今日好多人嗌港獨口號"},{"pid":"f0899e05860459db7ce21d1d832b88a4ca96d04d","tid":1806981,"uid":34869,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"384c9a54b3ca48360bce09ae441ee7ccc9508d16","tid":1806981,"uid":157522,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:03:35.000Z","msg":"雖然我同意有啲野係要靜靜地做<br />\n<br />\n我都覺，<br />\n怕係怕老一輩接受唔到會割"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:07:37.000Z","msg":"我本身都怕<br />\n因為獨旗今日會少左人出黎<br />\n但好明顯冇, 人數係第一樣野<br />\n第二樣野係經過既人對港獨既反應, 亦都唔係負面<br />\n然之後今日班狗做既野, 鳩拉同鳩射, 只會令市民乜都唔割<br />\n突破左心理關口就自然會繼續"},{"pid":"c6c6c5d4349c81c6ef54fb37191e99da5f35bed6","tid":1806981,"uid":34869,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"c4ecaeccf8e616a3eb83955e8a9e8071154ba9f6","tid":1806981,"uid":187201,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"今日好多人嗌港獨口號"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"好多人跟住叫<br />\n好激動<br />\n<br />\n16年天琦都係要就住就住講"},{"pid":"7808701683d15f3665f8e61b8885c19bcb1bc13d","tid":1806981,"uid":251366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:10:47.000Z","msg":"感動"},{"pid":"0649ceab5fcbf3182e367f07c1ff180ba1c6c788","tid":1806981,"uid":59297,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"係連登先會咁多打手屌<br />\n<br />\n港獨思潮<br />\n黃色經濟圈<br />\n組織工會<br />\n<br />\n將會係我地2020嘅抗爭目標，三者缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867712f52e9510966209960766104bab4a8685a2","tid":1806981,"uid":34869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0649ceab5fcbf3182e367f07c1ff180ba1c6c788","tid":1806981,"uid":59297,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"係連登先會咁多打手屌<br />\n<br />\n港獨思潮<br />\n黃色經濟圈<br />\n組織工會<br />\n<br />\n將會係我地2020嘅抗爭目標，三者缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈+工會<br />\n姐係經濟獨立<br />\n當你有錢, 唔駛睇人鼻息<br />\n就自然會為自己好"},{"pid":"97c095e56b896636f10714fbf7730448d22e4cab","tid":1806981,"uid":151074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:16: